{"tid":1259142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【眾籌】幫個忙，暫時唔好公開或傳閱同登報有關嘅未加密文件！！","createTime":"2019-06-26T13:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T01:44:45.000Z","uid":50983,"like":1407,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":175,"replies":[{"pid":"2307c29558f2eb4cc5f712f680bd6dada6f3b73d","tid":1259142,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"各位巴打：可唔可以請大家幫個忙，暫時唔好公開或傳閱同登報有關嘅未加密文件？由於部份報價已有更動，基於商業機密原則，相關合作夥伴現階段唔想全面性公開，人哋俾面我哋幫我哋度期度版面，我哋都想尊重返人哋機構既規條，方便大家合作。最後亦會於全部帳目結清後，交由第三方獨立會計師樓審核並向公眾公開。感激！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再一次感激各方幫咁多忙嘅人，無論寫手、翻譯、設計、法律，會計、寫網頁、搵報紙、公關、俾意見、捐錢、推post咩都好（希望我無漏），多謝多謝！！！！"},{"pid":"c0e581517096044d8446309fc4699bb923c2e3c1","tid":1259142,"uid":71270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:01:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b397679a76bc1d094aee29868fa5caf1629a04a","tid":1259142,"uid":268410,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"Facebook有人post左"},{"pid":"339d585ccea550c2940523f8c0343d257f2f5a75","tid":1259142,"uid":50983,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n〔突發！！〕給臺灣人的公開信公投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1258989/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1258989/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n而家臺灣個邊嘅公開信有兩個version，兩組人都俾咗好多心機去寫（真係好多謝咁多位寫手大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n因為都係大家嘅錢同行動，所以希望交番畀民眾決定，今晚11點截，我地會以多正皮者登報。<br />\n兩篇文會喺＃1同＃2，大家去正皮返你鐘意邊個啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（點都好，辛苦哂兩邊寫手！！！）"},{"pid":"b8db2096db64095ac5f4f21d790a42c854dae34a","tid":1259142,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b63c32f566bfe191586ccc64963e591165df298","tid":1259142,"uid":77199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d8734890d0941216a763e5bf73d2a758acde229","tid":1259142,"uid":216907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2307c29558f2eb4cc5f712f680bd6dada6f3b73d","tid":1259142,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"各位巴打：可唔可以請大家幫個忙，暫時唔好公開或傳閱同登報有關嘅未加密文件？由於部份報價已有更動，基於商業機密原則，相關合作夥伴現階段唔想全面性公開，人哋俾面我哋幫我哋度期度版面，我哋都想尊重返人哋機構既規條，方便大家合作。最後亦會於全部帳目結清後，交由第三方獨立會計師樓審核並向公眾公開。感激！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再一次感激各方幫咁多忙嘅人，無論寫手、翻譯、設計、法律，會計、寫網頁、搵報紙、公關、俾意見、捐錢、推post咩都好（希望我無漏），多謝多謝！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe6fa678a4b05cfce018fe54b35550638c2fba00","tid":1259142,"uid":162157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5912044e881efb2b7e0ec7d0bf7acab4edcba940","tid":1259142,"uid":110105,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"3b397679a76bc1d094aee29868fa5caf1629a04a","tid":1259142,"uid":268410,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"Facebook有人post左"},"citedBy":0,"